{"tid":1899890,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[AMD Yes!] AMD 將原本定位為 OEM 產品嘅 Ryzen 3 2300X 對外販售，六舊水都唔洗！","createTime":"2020-02-27T01:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T10:08:40.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a2a1fe90b7dcbf3d906365e56f99f57ddba6711f","tid":1899890,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T01:40:37.000Z","msg":"未知 AMD 是否要趁下一代 Ryzen 4000 系列發佈前將舊 U 快快「走鬼」，原本僅向 OEM 市場提供的二代 Ryzen 3 2300X 竟然「無啦啦」開放出來，仲以唔使 HK$600 賣街，難道 AMD 係想清走哂 12nm 二代 Zen+ 處理器嘅「死貨」??<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2018/07/source/1619160161473543263.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2018%2F07%2Fsource%2F1619160161473543263.jpg&h=48969f39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n根據 AMD 的資料，Ryzen 3 2300X 早在 2018 年 9 月 10 日就發佈，但原本僅為 OEM 渠道而生，Ryzen 3 2300X 基於 ZEN+ 架構、GlobalFoundries 12nm 工藝，採用 4 核心、4 線程設計，擁有 8MB L3 Cache、16 個 PCIe 3.0 通道，支援雙通道DDR4-2933 記憶體。Ryzen 3 2300X 的基礎時脈為 3.5GHz，Boost 時脈最高可達 4GHz，TDP 65W，隨 CPU 配連一個 AMD 原裝 Wraith Stealth 散熱器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/02/source/26172221411649317838.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F02%2Fsource%2F26172221411649317838.jpg&h=da850067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在硬體規格上，Ryzen 3 2300X 與 Intel Core i3-9100F 的定位相似，兩款產品同為 4 核心、4 線程設計，時脈方面 i3-9100F 較為優勝提供了 3.6GHz/4.2GHz，不過 2300X 就比 i3-9100F 擁有更大容量的 L3 Cache 及支援更高速度的記憶體時脈，至於售價就不用多說，肯定是 Ryzen 3 2300X 比較便宜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/19084/AMD_清死貨__12nm_二代_Zen%2B_走鬼_AMD_Ryzen_3_2300X_處理器_HK%24600_有找_\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F19084%2FAMD_%E6%B8%85%E6%AD%BB%E8%B2%A8__12nm_%E4%BA%8C%E4%BB%A3_Zen%252B_%E8%B5%B0%E9%AC%BC_AMD_Ryzen_3_2300X_%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8_HK%2524600_%E6%9C%89%E6%89%BE_&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplFgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=b08213f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/19084/AMD_清死貨__12nm_二代_Zen%2B_走鬼_AMD_Ryzen_3_2300X_處理器_HK%24600_有找_</a>"},{"pid":"f7d38a3e87f78f9cd4e076ac5ce3b538a14cd009","tid":1899890,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T01:41:34.000Z","msg":"根據 AMD 的消息，Ryzen 3 2300X 將於 3 月 3 日開賣，目前在馬來西亞 Lazada 網站標價為 298 馬幣 ( 69 美元 )，折合約港幣 547.99 元，不過在 Amazon 網站上列出的售價就高得不正常，高達 183.71 美元，折合約港幣 1,469.68，比 6 核心的 Ryzen 5 3600 的 174.99 美元還要貴，估計在正式開賣時會再調整價格。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/02/source/26171346261174593098.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F02%2Fsource%2F26171346261174593098.jpg&h=1b740d24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/02/source/2617134424755371.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F02%2Fsource%2F2617134424755371.jpg&h=ba9f3f1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec9121971f93b985969033dbbffc353a57229b5d","tid":1899890,"uid":316590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T02:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21ed96b5b33211d628b32077735cdc0e7bf819e","tid":1899890,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"2300X?<br />\n<br />\n要4C4T點解唔買3200?"},{"pid":"6bd9500b0ef27d29a70bd4dd56e116a8939ae414","tid":1899890,"uid":242278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b21ed96b5b33211d628b32077735cdc0e7bf819e","tid":1899890,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"2300X?<br />\n<br />\n要4C4T點解唔買3200?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T22:58:15.000Z","msg":"因為平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab8e058f11713a516c6403583f3fd7c9bc70c57","tid":1899890,"uid":52656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:01:49.000Z","msg":"買1600af版好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\"